{"tid":1264893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅集體出席婚禮直播容貌差很大網民：簡直是大型詐騙現場","createTime":"2019-06-29T02:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:34:28.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4c624c619af4f9cbb1b5d6ebaab6529ec0762c95","tid":1264893,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:11:26.000Z","msg":"網紅集體出席婚禮直播容貌差很大網民：簡直是大型詐騙現場 <br />\n<br />\n大陸人氣網紅韓安冉在微博上擁有百萬粉絲，剛滿20歲的她曾多次自爆自己的整形經歷，甚至還說會「活到老整到老」。話題性十足的她，近日和老公「小豬」決定要補辦婚禮，在婚禮的前一天，約了一批網紅好友舉辦單身派對，派對上不忘開直播和粉絲同樂，不料粉絲一看直播，竟發現平時照片都是美女的網紅們，在關掉濾鏡後一個個變了樣，讓不少人留言大喊「根本是大型詐騙現場」。<br />\n<br />\n網紅韓安冉15日舉辦婚前單身派對，邀請眾多網紅好友前來參加。由於派對現場由廠商贊助，因此每位網紅都要上台業配，但是當她們輪流走到台前直播時，在沒有濾鏡、特效修飾的情況下，長相竟全都變了樣，還有人在微博上截圖做出對比，讓大家發現網紅真相「差很大」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/19/1979159-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F1979159-XXL.jpg&h=89850024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友放出網紅自拍和直播的對比照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/19/1979161-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F1979161-XXL.jpg&h=32431a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從曝光的照片可見，這些網紅們不僅失去了大眼睛，就連皮膚也不再雪白、瓜子臉更是一秒變成大圓臉，讓觀看直播的粉絲難以置信。<br />\n<br />\n許多人見到她們的「真面目」後，紛紛讚嘆修圖軟體的偉大，更吐槽韓安冉的單身派對「根本是大型詐騙現場」、「我完全認不出來」、「沒濾鏡，全都現形了」，不過還是有粉絲力挺「明明各個都那麼瘦，角度問題吧」、「其實沒P的樣子也不難看」、「P圖都是難免的」。（編輯：藍詩孟）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/19/1979158-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F1979158-XXL.jpg&h=12204c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友放出網紅自拍和直播的對比照。（圖／翻攝自八组兔区吃瓜鹅微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/06/19/1979160-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F1979160-XXL.jpg&h=a9e6567b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/20/99/6455663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F20%2F99%2F6455663.jpg&h=82122c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/20/99/6455645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F20%2F99%2F6455645.jpg&h=6a8b0d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf1f98ef336e3ec2aaa63c336c4e9a7a8ee0ca51","tid":1264893,"uid":85180,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"唔知香港個D網紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0e3b50f18ce8726d922c0531929237a0eb2cdf","tid":1264893,"uid":181778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a708f2ec9521551617658d5c0f04168d8e71301e","tid":1264893,"uid":253343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf1f98ef336e3ec2aaa63c336c4e9a7a8ee0ca51","tid":1264893,"uid":85180,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"唔知香港個D網紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"不敢期待"},{"pid":"1c60bda6625c14d7ae25138fd87a24803d7b4ce6","tid":1264893,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5b5345cacace1aeac74791e2723d5e40960739","tid":1264893,"uid":70888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"大陸人真係智障<br />\n仲要咁多人睇<br />\n社會風氣真係垃圾"},{"pid":"351ec2a8044d886a16b80d3f0527684417cd6205","tid":1264893,"uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019